quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Taa Haa
  20,2,Men Telliniraali Alqur'aanaare nden e maa…óa fii yo a tampu
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonannde on huloowo [Alla]"
  20,4,Ko Jippinaande immorde e On Tagu…óo leydi ndin e kammuuli toowu…ói …óin
  20,5,Hinnorante On O fotii ka dow Arsi kin. @Corrected
  20,6,No woodani Mo ko woni kon e kammuuli …óin e ko woni kon e leydi nden e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji …ói…ói e ko woni kon ka ley leydi
  20,7,"Si a fen√±inii konngol ngol, pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi gunndoo on e ko o suu…ói"
  20,8,"Alla rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko, no woodani Mo In…óe Mo∆¥∆¥e …óen"
  20,9,taw si arii e maa…óa Yewtere fii Muusaa
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'unoo yiite, o wi'ani …ìeynguure makko nden: \"√ëii…ìee, min dey mi haynike jaynge bela-jo'o mi addanay on immorde e magge docotal maa…óum mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo"
  20,11,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge o noddaa; \"ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko Min Woni Joomi maa…óa solu pa…óe maa …óen; pellet an, hi…óa ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa La…ì…ìinaande(seninangol)"
  20,13,Min Mi Su…ìike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede kon
  20,14,"Pellet, ko Min Woni Alla rewetee…óo alaa si wonaa Min Rewam; √±ii…ìir e Julde nden fii Annditugol lam"
  20,15,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aroowal Mi…óo …óe…ìa suu…óude ngal fii yo…ìe kala wonkii ko ki huuwi kon"
  20,16,Wata faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gom- …óinaa ngal o jokki mbelee…óe makko o halkii
  20,17,Ko hon…óum woni ka √±aamo maa…óa an Muusaa
  20,18,"O maaki: \"Ndun ko tuggordu am mi…óo tuggoo ndu mi…óo liwtirana ndu dammi am …óin, mi…óo mari kadi haajuuji goo e mayru"
  20,19,"O Daali: \"Li…ìu ndu, an Muusaa"
  20,20,"O li…ìi ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mboddi wonundi yahude"
  20,21,"O Daali: \"Nanngu ndu wata a hulu Men artiray ndu e mbaadi mayru araniri ndin"
  20,22,Ukku junngo maa…óa ngon ka nder jiiba maa; ngo yaltay ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e bone …óum ko Aaya goo
  20,23,Fii yo Men hollle immorde e Aayeeje Amen Maw…óe …óen
  20,24,"Yahu ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,25,"O maaki: \"Jooma Yan√±anam …ìernde am nden"
  20,26,Newinanaa lam fiyaake am on
  20,27,Firtaa finnde nden ka …óenngal am
  20,28,Fii yo …ìe faamu konngol am ngol
  20,29,Wa…óanaa lam ballo jeyaa…óo ka …ìeynguure am
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musi…ó…óo am on"
  20,31,Semmbinir mo darnde am
  20,32,Tawnaa mo e nder fiyaake am on
  20,33,Fii yo men Senine ko …óuu…ói
  20,34,Men ja≈ãtoMaa ko …óuu…ói
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Wonii Humpitii…óo Men"
  20,36,"O Daali: \"Gom…óii a okkaama toraare maa…óa nden an Muusaa"
  20,37,Gom…óii Men Neeminiino ma e laawol goo
  20,38,Tuma nde Men Wahayinnoo faade e yumma maa ko Wahayinaa kon
  20,39,"[Men Daali] Bugo mo ka nder hontoore bugo…óaa nden kadi ka nder diidere, yo diidere nden kadi bugoyo mo ka fonngo; ∆¥etta mo ga√±o Am e ga√±o makko, Mi werlii e maa…óa Giggol immorde ka Am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndenka Am"
  20,40,"Tuma nde banndiraawo maa…óa on yahaynoo; o wi'a: \"Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?\" Men artirmaa ka yumma maa…óa fii yo gite makko …óen …ìuu…ìu hara o sunaaki. Waru…óaa wonkii Men danndumaa immorde e sa…óteende nden, Men jarribimaa jarrabuyeeje √±ii…ìu…óaa duu…ìi ka yim…ìe Madyana refti aru…óaa ka fodoore ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,41,Mi Su…ìimaa fii hoore-Am
  20,42,Yahu an e musi…ó…óo maa on wonndude e Aayeeje Am …óen wata on derfu e ja≈ãtagol Lam
  20,43,"Yahee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,44,Wi'anee mo konngol newiingol bela-jo'o kanko o waajitoto maa…óum o hula
  20,45,"∆Åe maaki: \"Joomi amen, menen dey me…óen huli nde murtata e hoore amen maa nde o bewata"
  20,46,"O Daali: \"Wata on hulu, pellet, Min Mi…óo wonndi e moo…óon Mi…óo Nana Mi…óo Yi'a"
  20,47,"Aree ka makko, wi'on: \"Menen ko Men Nulaa…ìe Joomi maa…óa, accitu wonndude e amen …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen wata a leptu …ìe, gom…óii men addanii ma Aaya immorde ka Joomi maa…óa, kisiyee on wonii e on jokku…óo Peewal ngal"
  20,48,"Gom…óii Wahayinaama e amen; wonndema, Lepte …óen no fawii ka fennu…óo …óuuri"
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi moo…óon"
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Joomi amen, ko On Okku…óo kala huunde tagu mayre ngun refti O Fewni"
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko honno gire arane …óen fewndori"
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ganndal …óum no ka Joomi am e nder Deftere, Joomi am majjataa O yejjitataa"
  20,53,"On wa…óan…óo on leydi ndin we∆¥∆¥itaandi, o naadani on e nder mayri laawi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngun ndiyam Men yaltiniri …óam nooneeji immorde e pu…ói sertu…ói"
  20,54,"√ëaamee aynon neemoraa…ói mo'on …óim. Pellet, no e nder …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- …ìe hakkillaaji …óin"